---
title: Easy Cheesy BBQ Beef & Pork Filo Pie with Baby Leaves & Sesame Seeds
description: Indulge in this mouth-watering creation, where tender beef and pork mince intertwines with melty cheese, all encased in crisp, flaky filo. This fusion of flavours promises a memorable feast, making every bite a perfect blend of comfort and gourmet sophistication!
